data.description: Beautiful home on a corner lot in Stockdale Ranch neighborhood. Kitchen has stainless steel appliances with brand new dishwasher and granite counters. Wood laminate and tile flooring downstairs. Wood blinds on all dual pane windows and upgraded chandeliers and light fixtures throughout. Home is move-in ready and perfect for a large or growing family! New shopping center and restaurants being developed just down the road. Spacious patio in the backyard and a large balcony off of the master bedroom upstairs. Beautiful gardens full of fresh flowers. This home has a ton of storage space as well. Master has two walk-in closets, indoor laundry room and giant pantry! Don't miss out on this spectacular home in a great neighborhood with  amazing schools!
